commit_message:
Update backup state when guest error occurs

Reason:
  - When guest error appears at 'create_backup'
    stage, backup still remain in NEW state.
  - only two types of exceptions can appear:
    - remote timeput, leads to GuestError;
    - unreachable AMPQ service from taskmanager site.

Changes:
  - updating status when guest error appears;
  - updating backup model with a new method;
  - adding test;

Change-Id: I05f5caea4380edbe0e8bebc618ecfb52afe45872
Closes-Bug: #1333659

Add neutron-based configuration for Trove

Reasons:
 - Trove can work with Neutron by setting specific configurations to trove-*.conf:
   - network_label_regex;
   - ip_regex;
   - black_list_regex;
   - default_neutron_networks;
   - network_driver;

Changes:
 - enable Neutron integration for Trove if Neutron service is enabled.

Change-Id: I5fb3a3bd23e66bf6eeb20321d45e6b8ec39b0abd
